definitions.definition: To brew one's beer or other alcoholic beverage at home.
To create something as an enthusiast, rather than using a commercial option.
To jailbreak a video game console, specifically made by Nintendo, to run unofficial programs.

main_definition: To brew one's beer or other alcoholic beverage at home.
secondary_definitions: ( informal ) To create something as an enthusiast, rather than using a commercial option.
( gaming ) To jailbreak a video game console, specifically made by Nintendo, to run unofficial programs.
